entries.complete: All waves destroyed. You have performed your duty well. Return to your superior officer for additional assignments.
entries.dd_boss_taunt_1: You dare challenge the might of Coyn?
entries.dd_boss_taunt_3: Don't worry, this won't take long.
entries.dd_boss_taunt_5: You shall have a noble death!
entries.found_loc: Located another area of high enemy activity.
entries.level_boss: %TO has been eliminated. Nice work, pilot.
entries.level_boss_dead: Very nice work. Coynite's respect their champions and you have gained respect in their eyes for defeating one of them.
entries.level_increase: Be alert! The Coynite Mercenaries are become more aggressive.
entries.quest_destroy_d: Destroy all Coynite ships you can find. If you do well enough the Coynite will send their best pilots after you.
entries.quest_location_d: Travel to the Dathomir system and you will receive Nav waypoints to areas of high Coynite concentrations.
entries.targets_behind: pcontrast1 Tactical Computer:pcontrast3 <Warning! Enemy ships detected. Incoming from the rear.>
entries.targets_detected: pcontrast1 Tactical Computer:pcontrast3 <Alert! Enemy ships engaging weapons and incoming at attack speeds.>
entries.taunt_3: Prepare to be embraced by death.
entries.taunt_4: You should not have done that.
entries.taunt_5: Perhaps you wish to rethink your actions?
entries.title: Dathomir System: Destroy the Coynite Fighters Duty
entries.title_d: Travel to the Dathomir system and destroy the Coynite fighters. The Coynite problem has begun to become out of hand. In order to protect Dathomir the Coynite numbers must be reduced.
